<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (dạymaⁿạ btkẖbyny ... lmạ thb ạlryḥ
 bjnạḥk tdạryny .. wʿdk wʿd ṣryḥ)2
 1- (lmạ ạlnạs tnsạny .. wạsẖʿr ạ̹ny wḥyd
 ạ̉ṣrkẖ lk fy mkạny .. tyjy bḥb ạ̉kyd)2
 (wtnsyny wtʿzyny)2 .. yạ yswʿ
 2- (lmạ ạlnạs tḥạrbny .. bạlạ̹ymạn bạlqạk
 ṣwtk yndh ạbny .. ạ̉jry wạbạt fy ḥmạk)2
 (wtnsyny wtʿzyny)2 .. yạ yswʿ
 3- (lmạ ạlnạs bthyny .. wạrjʿ wạnạ mjrwḥ
 bṣlybk btʿyny .. wysẖjʿny ạlrwḥ)2
 (wtnsyny wtʿzyny)2 .. yạ yswʿ</lyrics>
